<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN""http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/loose.dtd"><HTML lang="ja"><html><head><title>Grammar Quiz</title><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><style type="text/css"><!--.style1 {color: #FF00FF}--></style></head><!-- created by Fred Bickerstaff --> <script LANGUAGE="javascript" type="text/JavaScript">		var numQuestions = 6;		var numAnswered = 0;		var numCorrect = 0;		var q_id=201;			</script><SCRIPT LANGUAGE="JavaScript" SRC="../../../../js/quiz_top.js"></SCRIPT><LINK href="../../../../css/particleQuiz.css" type=text/css rel=stylesheet><body class="backgroundColor"><h2 class="titleText" align="center"> ぶんぽうクイズ </h2><div class="backgroundLayer" align="center" id="quiz"><div class="innerTitle">611D Yookoso II Chapter 3 〜し方 (How to do something)</div><div class="quizlistLine"><a href="../../../../gquiz.php">Return    to Practice Quizzes list page</a></div> <p class="instructionLine">Conjugate the word in the (   ) to say "how to do ...".　write「かた」in Kanji.  <FORM name="quiz">	<! Question 1>	<div class="questionLineOdd"><b>1. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;この&nbsp;&nbsp;	<INPUT name="answer" type="text" onChange="checkAnswer('かんじの書き方_漢字の書き方',this.value,0)" style="width: 150px;">    </INPUT>を教えてください。（かんじを書く）	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>	<! Question 2>	<div class="questionLineEven"><b>2. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;おいしいコーヒーの&nbsp;&nbsp;	<INPUT name="answer" type="text" onChange="checkAnswer('入れ方',this.value,1)" style="width: 150px;">    </INPUT>を知っていますか。〔入れる）	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>				<! Question 3>	<div class="questionLineOdd"><b>3. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;あの人は、&nbsp;&nbsp;	<INPUT name="answer" type="text" onChange="checkAnswer('はしの使い方',this.value,2)" style="width: 150px;">    </INPUT>が上手ですね。（はしを使う）	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>			<! Question 4>	<div class="questionLineEven"><b>4. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;	<INPUT name="answer" type="text" onChange="checkAnswer('車の運転のし方_車の運転の仕方',this.value,3)" style="width: 150px;">    </INPUT>はどこに書いてありますか。〔車を運転する）	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>				<! Question 5>	<div class="questionLineOdd"><b>5. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;あの人は		<INPUT name="answer" type="text" onChange="checkAnswer('はしの持ち方_箸の持ち方',this.value,4)" style="width: 150px;">	</SELECT>が下手ですね。（はしを持つ）	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>	<! Question 6>	<div class="questionLineEven"><b>6. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;	<INPUT name="answer" type="text" onChange="checkAnswer('デパートへの行き方',this.value,5)" style="width: 150px;">    </INPUT>をおしえてください。〔デパートへ行く）	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>			</FORM><div id="score"></div><div><table class="optionBox"><tr>	<td><BUTTON onClick="checkAnswers()">Check Answers</BUTTON></td>	<td><BUTTON onClick="resetValues()">Reset Values</BUTTON></td></tr></table></div></div></body></html>